GSD.product_version: versions from v5.14 to before v5.15.91
GSD.description:
net: stmmac: enable all safety features by default

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.91 by commit 120b8e527e07c65de7f2b9018dcd9d17e66f2427, it was introduced in version v5.14 by commit 5ac712dcdfefb1a783384db85e0507d161e87812. For more details please see the references link.
